    seed=42,           # Random seed for reproducibility
    max_steps=100      # Episode length limit
)
```

### Task Parameters

```python
task = HardFullOperationsTask(
    max_steps=120      # Difficulty: more steps = easier
)
```

### Agent Parameters

```python
agent = BaselineAgent(
    seed=42            # Baseline uses deterministic keyword matching
)
